1760:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     This section provides functions allowing to:
1761:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****       (+) Configure the commutation event in case of use of the Hall sensor interface.
1762:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****       (+) Configure Output channels for OC and PWM mode.
